PART 6: DAX QUERY PATTERNS FOR THE 10 QUESTION TYPES

Pattern 1 - Active facilities by type and location:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name], 'CurMonData'[City], 'CurMonData'[Country Name], 'CurMonData'[Region], 'CurMonData'[Main usage type]), 'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated] = "Active", 'CurMonData'[Commercial / Housing] = "Commercial", 'CurMonData'[Country Name] = "Australia")

Pattern 2 - Net Book Value by location:
EVALUATE ROW("Total NBV", [Value_NBV])
Or filtered: EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonNBV'[Name of Architectural Object], 'CurMonNBV'[City], "NBV", SUM('CurMonNBV'[Current Year NBV])), 'CurMonNBV'[City] = "Comodoro Rivadavia")

Pattern 3 - Asset register by location:
EVALUATE FILTER('Need Attention', 'Need Attention'[City] = "Comodoro Rivadavia")
Or: EVALUATE SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Need Attention'[Arch.Obj. ID], 'Need Attention'[Name of Architectural Object], 'Need Attention'[Street], 'Need Attention'[City], 'Need Attention'[Region])

Pattern 4 - ROU value:
EVALUATE ROW("Total ROU", [Value_ROU])

Pattern 5 - Active contracts:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Contract No and Name], 'CurMonData'[Term End], 'CurMonData'[Site and Name], 'CurMonData'[Country Name]), 'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated] = "Active")

Pattern 6 - Facilities by PSL:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Billing File'[Region], 'Billing File'[Country], 'Billing File'[Facility Name]), 'Billing File'[PSL Name] = "Cementing")

Pattern 7 - Facilities by building type:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name], 'CurMonData'[City], 'CurMonData'[Country Name], 'CurMonData'[Main usage type]), 'CurMonData'[Main usage type] = "Warehouse")

Pattern 8 - Operating expense:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Billing File'[Facility Name], 'Billing File'[PSL Name], "Cost", SUM('Billing File'[Allocated USD]), "FT2", SUM('Billing File'[Billable FT2])), 'Billing File'[Country] = "Australia")

Pattern 9 - Expense by category:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(ROW("Rental", [Rental Expense - Current Year], "Depreciation", [Depreciation - Current Year], "Janitorial", [Janitorial - Current Year], "Insurance", [Insurance - Current Year], "Total", [Total Current Year Expenses YTD]), 'CurMonData'[Country Name] = "Australia")

Pattern 10 - Risk summary:
EVALUATE ROW("Expired", [Count_Expired_Contract], "Expired No SR", [Count_Expired_Contract_No_SR], "Active on Terminated", [Count_ActContr_on_TermSite], "Leased No Contract", [Count_ActLeasedSite_No_Contract], "Total Contracts", [Count_Contract], "NBV", [Value_NBV], "ROU", [Value_ROU])


